Drifter is the ExpressionEngine 2.x version of Gypsy, which was originally developed by Brandon Kelly.

Drifter extends Core EE classes, which is not officially supported by EllisLab. Use with caution.

Please do not contact Brian Litzinger or Brandon Kelly directly about support for Drifter. Please use http://devot-ee.com/add-ons/support/drifter/viewforum/320/. Brian may occassionally view the forum, but he does not actively support Drifter.